For the Pizza Dough –
1.5 cups All Purpose Flour
1.5 tsp Active Instant Dry Yeast
1/2 cup Warm Water
1 tsp Sugar
1/2 tsp Salt
1 tbsp olive oil
For the Pizza –
4 tbsp Pizza Sauce
1/3 cup Veggie Toppings (Onion,Capsicum, Sweet corn and Tomatoes)
1/4 cup Mozzarella Cheese (or as needed)
1-2 tsp olive oil
Dried Mixed Italian Herbs (for topping)
Dried Chilli Flakes (for topping)
